  "abstract": "A brief description of 7 pigeon pea diseases prevalent in China is given. These were the fusarium wilt (caused by Fusarium udum), phytopthora blight (caused by Phytopthora drechsleri f.sp. cajani), powdery mildew (Oidiopsis taurica [Leveillula taurica]), sterility mosaic, cercospora leaf spot (Cercospora spp.), rust (caused by Uredo cajani) and phoma stem canker (caused by Phoma cajani). Suggested measures for controlling pigeon pea diseases in China are tabulated.",
